In this i am going to explain about the basic tutorial of java langugae.
First of all java was created by james goosling. Java as named after a oak tree.Java is called as programming language. What do you meant by a program? A program is a set of operations to perform.Where can we perform all 
these? A platform it is a software or hardware in which a program runs.Everything in java is class based.The main applications of java are *Desktop apps,*Mobile applications,*Embedded systems,*Entrprise Apps,*Smartcard,*Robotics.
Java has three editions 1.Java Standard Edition 2)Java Entrprise Edition 3) Jva MicroEdition.
